VE", "id": "318942890891773"}]}, "change_log": "Changes:\n- Exchanged player starts in the stadium, the player can now restart the game without getting teleported\n- Balls don't collide with each other anymore\n\nPerformance Improvements:\n- Reduced texture sizes\n- Improved memory load\n- Improved hand-tracking collision tracking, it now feels more natural", "created_date": 1730794768, "id": "6855461314577670", "version": "1.3.2", "version_code": 44, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6855460434577758"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5211598935630591", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "6855461314577670"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "318942890891773"}]}, "change_log": "Version 1.3 now includes:\n\n- Full support for hand-tracking\n- The current tutorial also supports hand-tracking\n- Tutorial only opens up on the first play, after that it can be opened via the menu\n- new menu design\n- adapted existing Buttons to be more accessible for Hand-Tracking\n- added \"join our testing-channel\" Banner\n- exchanged old player movement with teleportation\n- performance improvements", "created_date": 1729878729, "id": "6800498533407282", "version": "1.3", "version_code": 43, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "6800497740074028"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}